column1: Ryan Howard from the temp agency. Daniqua sent me down to start today.
I heard they might be closing this branch down. Thats just the rumor going around. This is my first day. I dont really know.
Whats up? Nice to meet you.
You shouldve put him in custardy.
I downloaded it on her computer. I hope she doesnt mind. She just had a lot of extra space.
Oh, no, the girl in the... sketch.
Did you get the kind with the cookies? Instead of the...
But, Im getting paid to skip lunch?
Can we just do one? Thats cool, thats fine.
Im installing File Share on all the computers.
You dont want to recycle them?
What about this bottle of power drink?
No, this is Rite Aid Night Swept.
Wow. How many filet-o-fishes did you eat?
